{"word":"Jehu","slug":"jehu","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jehu</b> <a href=\"#/H3058\">H3058</a> <br/> 1. The prophet who announced the wrath of Jehovah against Baasha, king of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=1'>1Ki 16:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=7'>1Ki 16:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=12'>1Ki 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=19&verse=2'>2Ch 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=34'>2Ch 20:34</a><br/> 2. Son of Nimshi, king of Israel<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=16'>1Ki 19:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=14'>2Ki 9:14</a> <br/> - Religious zeal of, in slaying idolaters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=37'>2Ki 9:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=28'>2Ki 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=9'>2Ch 22:9</a> <br/> - His territory invaded by Hazael, king of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=33'>2Ki 10:33</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=17'>1Ki 19:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=30'>2Ki 10:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=12'>2Ki 15:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=4'>Hos 1:4</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=35'>2Ki 10:35</a> <br/> 3. Son of Obed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=38'>1Ch 2:38</a><br/> 4. Son of Josibiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=35'>1Ch 4:35</a><br/> 5. A Benjamite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=3'>1Ch 12:3</a>"}]}